# ============================================

# COLLECTION STRUCTURE (MongoDB Style)

# ============================================

Instead of:

* geo table
* address table
* company table
* users table

We embed them like this:

```
users
 ├── name
 ├── username
 ├── email
 ├── phone
 ├── website
 ├── address
 │     ├── street
 │     ├── suite
 │     ├── city
 │     ├── zipcode
 │     └── geo
 │           ├── lat
 │           └── lng
 └── company
       ├── name
       ├── catchPhrase
       └── bs
```

