# ============================================

# Sample Test Queries

# ============================================

## 🔍 Find All Users

```javascript
db.users.find().pretty()
```

## 🔍 Find User by City

```javascript
db.users.find({ "address.city": "Gwenborough" })
```

## 🔍 Find by Company Name

```javascript
db.users.find({ "company.name": "Deckow-Crist" })
```

## 🔍 Update Salary

```javascript
db.employees.updateOne(
  { employee_code: "EMP101" },
  { $set: { salary: 65000 } }
)
```

## 🔍 Delete User

```javascript
db.users.deleteOne({ username: "Bret" })
```

